---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Home"
  description="Forge orchestrates teams of AI agents to complete complex engineering work — reliably, transparently, and at a pace no single model can match."
>
  <article class="page-article">

    <header class="page-hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">AI-native engineering orchestration</p>
        <h1 class="hero-headline">
          Ship faster with<br class="headline-break" /> an AI agent team.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subhead">
          Forge sends specialist AI agents to plan, build, test, and review your engineering work —
          then gives you a structured record of everything they did.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/what-forge-does" class="cta-primary">What Forge does &rarr;</a>
          <a href="/how-forge-runs-work" class="cta-secondary">How it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="highlights-section" aria-labelledby="highlights-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h2 id="highlights-heading" class="section-heading">The short version</h2>
        <div class="highlights-grid">
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3 class="highlight-heading">Plans before it builds</h3>
            <p class="highlight-body">
              A planning agent reads your brief and writes a step-by-step implementation plan.
              You approve before any code is written.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3 class="highlight-heading">Right agent for each job</h3>
            <p class="highlight-body">
              Architect, engineer, test-engineer, red — each specialist gets exactly the context it needs.
              No context overload, no hallucinated context.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3 class="highlight-heading">Adversarial review built in</h3>
            <p class="highlight-body">
              "Red" agents read completed work specifically to find problems.
              Work only advances when it passes the review gate.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3 class="highlight-heading">Complete audit trail</h3>
            <p class="highlight-body">
              Every decision, plan, diff, and gate approval is stored locally.
              Inspect exactly what happened, and why.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nav-section" aria-labelledby="nav-heading">
      <div class="section-inner section-inner--narrow section-inner--centered">
        <h2 id="nav-heading" class="section-heading">Learn more</h2>
        <div class="nav-cards">
          <a href="/what-forge-does" class="nav-card">
            <span class="nav-card-label">Stakeholders &amp; teams</span>
            <span class="nav-card-title">What Forge does</span>
            <span class="nav-card-desc">Plain-language overview of what Forge is and why orchestration matters.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/how-forge-runs-work" class="nav-card">
            <span class="nav-card-label">Engineers</span>
            <span class="nav-card-title">How Forge runs work</span>
            <span class="nav-card-desc">Runs, tasks, gates, reds, agents, and the SQLite blackboard explained.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/docs/" class="nav-card">
            <span class="nav-card-label">Reference</span>
            <span class="nav-card-title">Documentation</span>
            <span class="nav-card-desc">Operator docs, CLI reference, and configuration guides.</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>
</MarketingLayout>

<style>
  .page-article {
    color: var(--forge-color-text);
    font-family: var(--forge-font-family-body);
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-base);
    line-height: var(--forge-line-height-relaxed);
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */

  .page-hero {
    background: var(--forge-color-surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--forge-color-border);
    padding: var(--forge-space-20) var(--forge-space-6) var(--forge-space-16);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--forge-layout-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--forge-color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--forge-space-4);
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-family: var(--forge-font-family-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--forge-font-size-3xl), 5vw, var(--forge-font-size-5xl));
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--forge-color-text-strong);
    margin: 0 0 var(--forge-space-6);
  }

  .headline-break {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .headline-break {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .hero-subhead {
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-lg);
    color: var(--forge-color-text-muted);
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin: 0 0 var(--forge-space-8);
    line-height: var(--forge-line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--forge-space-3);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--forge-space-3) var(--forge-space-6);
    background: var(--forge-color-accent);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: var(--forge-radius-md);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-base);
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: var(--forge-color-accent-bright);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--forge-space-3) var(--forge-space-6);
    color: var(--forge-color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: var(--forge-radius-md);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-base);
    border: 1px solid var(--forge-color-border);
    transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    color: var(--forge-color-text-strong);
    border-color: var(--forge-color-accent);
  }

  /* ── Highlights ── */

  .highlights-section {
    padding: var(--forge-space-16) var(--forge-space-6);
    background: var(--forge-color-surface-raised);
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: var(--forge-layout-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-inner--narrow {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .section-inner--centered {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--forge-font-family-display);
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--forge-color-text-strong);
    margin: 0 0 var(--forge-space-8);
  }

  .highlights-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--forge-space-6);
  }

  .highlight {
    background: var(--forge-color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--forge-color-border);
    border-radius: var(--forge-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--forge-space-6);
  }

  .highlight-heading {
    font-family: var(--forge-font-family-display);
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--forge-color-text-strong);
    margin: 0 0 var(--forge-space-3);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--forge-color-accent);
    padding-left: var(--forge-space-3);
  }

  .highlight-body {
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-sm);
    color: var(--forge-color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: var(--forge-line-height-relaxed);
  }

  /* ── Nav section ── */

  .nav-section {
    padding: var(--forge-space-16) var(--forge-space-6);
  }

  .nav-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--forge-space-4);
    margin-top: var(--forge-space-8);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .nav-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--forge-space-2);
    background: var(--forge-color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--forge-color-border);
    border-radius: var(--forge-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--forge-space-6);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
  }

  .nav-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--forge-color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px hsl(329 65% 50% / 0.10);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .nav-card-label {
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--forge-color-accent);
  }

  .nav-card-title {
    font-family: var(--forge-font-family-display);
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--forge-color-text-strong);
  }

  .nav-card-desc {
    font-size: var(--forge-font-size-sm);
    color: var(--forge-color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--forge-line-height-relaxed);
  }
</style>
